？"},{"pid":"c082950f82743fd64ebbe4d58aa5366aefa544be","tid":1365121,"uid":129243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2ec30d449251da43dc7a3f290e480c11b527b1","tid":1365121,"uid":277125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6fc967db994ad472ff66a7d5895955428bbc1af","tid":1365121,"uid":60070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:47:22.000Z","msg":"記得上各區地政處去告示板睇下有無鄉黑申請丁屋，見一間反對一間"},{"pid":"9275e112bf86a9b505775871e5e607fd4ca75dbc","tid":1365121,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c94c5a2597c12ddf5232fab682b72ed707b46e","tid":1365121,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:48:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8beae4e0ff277df909c1644d18d77437d6dda071","tid":1365121,"uid":289120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"452449fa18236e3c7433a986085668a1af0acaf8","tid":1365121,"uid":228645,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"痴q線<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求一樣都未爭取到就改變運動重點?<br />\n明明成功在眼前<br />\n建制開始愈來愈多聲音支持獨立調查同淋病下台<br />\n<br />\n咁對得住之前死咗/拉咗想我地幫佢地堅持落去嘅兄弟咩"},{"pid":"0b5e4fcd08eab677be7f6d76ffcaa9fdea9f1b14","tid":1365121,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"佢話唔好full gear入元朗<br />\n我唔應同<br />\n擺明727 港共政權會再set局傷害示威者<br />\n雖然奶野既大佬著哂草<br />\n安家費某辦公室又無找數<br />\n何孝子又過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n但元朗係不乏無腦廢老響應上星期恐襲<br />\n仲有預計元朗狗屋一定會被人圍<br />\n換言之有兩個可能<br />\n<br />\n1 係班狗元朗重兵拆散遊行隊伍再一班藍屍孤狼式抽水 (人少既話)<br />\n<br />\n2 人多過百萬既話， 班狗哩翻哂入狗屋， 再等班喪屍出黎咬人甚至拎刀， 通渠水突襲而班狗唔出黎拉人<br />\n<br />\n所以727 一定要出， 仲要full gear同組衛隊<br />\n做埋班狗果份<br />\n甚至將當日既犯罪份子以及證據keep住<br />\n唔報警同直接將證據送到去中立國or國際法庭<br />\n突顯港共誠信破產"},{"pid":"c860f1e79dd885f0301ac08bb592e7b224ac01be","tid":1365121,"uid":276548,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:39:38.000Z","msg":"佢正宗冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個怕事既和理非"},{"pid":"09f8fc8788d87daffc3fcede27b9d2131a91a02f","tid":1365121,"uid":59989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ad8a62ac06a285b8c1954d30ddf2eb6dd5b2ac9","tid":1365121,"uid":149833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"掀起連串示威嘅五大訴求呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T05:43:37.000Z","msg":"五大訴求同反警黑係無衝突<br />\n但最終目標係一樣<br />\n但反警黑可以呼應更多支持者<br />\n有更高既道德高地<br />\n警黑調查到底 絕對直擊黑警、政府心臟同林鄭<br />\n當政、警收皮時<br />\n五大訴求自然會得到回應"}]}